    "For instance, Stonier and Adarkwah (2023) observed significant improvements in teachers' interest, perception, and self-efficacy in STEM following professional development sessions.",
    "Nevertheless, their study's focus was limited to preservice early childhood teachers, indicating a need for broader research across different teaching levels and disciplines.",
    "• This research gap is evident in several areas.",
    "A study by Stonier and Adarkwah (2023) revealed significant improvements in teachers' interest in STEM, perceptions of STEM, and self-efficacy following professional development programs.",
